        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Pell Grant Sustainability Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Education to calculate the award amount for Pell Grants for award year 2020&#8211;2021 and each subsequent award year by indexing the award amount to the rate of inflation.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
